messages.subject: Top Misconceptions
messages.msgSnippet: Hey all. I just joined and hope to learn more about Samurai s and Japanese history. The home page directs us to the Top Misconceptions about Samurai s page and
messages.messageBody:
Hey all. I just joined and hope to learn more about Samurai's and
Japanese history. The home page directs us to the Top Misconceptions
about Samurai's page and I do believe it would be very helpful.
However there is this annoying Yahoo Geosites box in the middle of the
page which will not go away and thus I cant read the topics of the
page. Does anyone else have this problem? For all the times I have to
type in those little codes that supposedly keep spam out you would
think Yahoo would keep their own junk off too!
